          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Deterring Espionage by Foreign Entities through National Defense Act of 2018 or the DEFEND Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes changes to provisions governing federal civil claims for trade secret misappropriation.</p> <p>Specifically, it does the following: </p> <ul> <li>increases punitive damages for a victim, </li> <li>extends the statute of limitations for filing a claim, and </li> <li>allows claims for conduct that occurs outside the United States if the offense causes substantial economic harm in the United States.</li> </ul>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-12-12T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
